            "title": "Population Structure of a Cave-Dwelling Bat, Miniopterus schreibersii: Does It Reflect History and Social Organization?",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Maria João",
                    "lastName": "Ramos Pereira"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Patrícia",
