            "title": "PHYSICAL CONDITIONS AND MICROCLIMATE OF TWO Cynopterus SPECIES ROOSTS IN AN ABANDONED VILLAGE IN LAMBOR, PERAK",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "name": "Universiti Sains Malaysia"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Mohd Rani",
